    "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/71d09c949402e562e6c88bb366816529.avif?t=1745450635\" width=540 height=172 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >El juego.</h2><br>Las almas de los muertos han quedado atrapadas en una dimensión similar al Purgatorio, donde se ven obligadas a luchar entre sí para tener la oportunidad de escapar. Sigue al grupo principal mientras afrontan peligros y enemigos exóticos, hacen aliados, y aprenden más sobre la verdadera naturaleza de la competencia en su búsqueda por recuperar su libertad.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/57d5cd7caf53de3e75ea4511f3074ac7.poster.avif?t=1745450635\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/57d5cd7caf53de3e75ea4511f3074ac7.webm?t=1745450635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/57d5cd7caf53de3e75ea4511f3074ac7.mp4?t=1745450635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Características.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/05873e08e380d0458df45215730404ff.poster.avif?t=1745450635\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/05873e08e380d0458df45215730404ff.webm?t=1745450635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/05873e08e380d0458df45215730404ff.mp4?t=1745450635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Sistema de combate de batalla de tiempo activo (BTA).<br></li><li> 3 personajes principales con atributos, destrezas y mejoras únicas para adaptarse a tu estrategia preferida.<br></li><li> Juego enfocado en torno a la historia.<br></li><li> Elige tus peleas en la Arena.<br></li><li> Mima a un dinosaurio. </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/79f911303695c9a7d853bf698a10a98c.poster.avif?t=1745450635\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/79f911303695c9a7d853bf698a10a98c.webm?t=1745450635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/79f911303695c9a7d853bf698a10a98c.mp4?t=1745450635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>¡Demo disponible ahora!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/fad60b67e29773ecf3084037e64e2897.poster.avif?t=1745450635\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/fad60b67e29773ecf3084037e64e2897.webm?t=1745450635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/fad60b67e29773ecf3084037e64e2897.mp4?t=1745450635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
